divs: Sighting Detailsi was out on my front balcony with my room-mate, when i saw this blue glowing orb moving sporadically in the sky. When it moved it left a trail behind it like when you move a flashlight in a photograph. i thought " I must be crazy, this is the weirdest thing i have ever seen". it only lasted a few seconds and i never returned.
